    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/74c2d0b9acdccf36a105cb627fce5e66.poster.avif?t=1737819779\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/74c2d0b9acdccf36a105cb627fce5e66.webm?t=1737819779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/74c2d0b9acdccf36a105cb627fce5e66.mp4?t=1737819779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >垃圾清理模拟器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采取行动拯救我们的星球！在这款独特的模拟游戏中，通过清理世界各地的污染地区来领导一场提高环保意识的运动。清洁从海滩到火车站、公园到河流的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/7abc99cd6f1e30cd2a227e782adbdf35.poster.avif?t=1737819779\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/7abc99cd6f1e30cd2a227e782adbdf35.webm?t=1737819779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/7abc99cd6f1e30cd2a227e782adbdf35.mp4?t=1737819779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特征：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >清理现实地点的环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过在游戏内社交媒体上直播来收集捐款</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩大和管理您的团队</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捐款购买新装备并进行世界巡演</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成有趣的任务，同时提高环保意识</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/85811bd19f4dd8dfbc4a4e0c39958706.poster.avif?t=1737819779\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/85811bd19f4dd8dfbc4a4e0c39958706.webm?t=1737819779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262450/extras/85811bd19f4dd8dfbc4a4e0c39958706.mp4?t=1737819779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救世界就在你的手中！立即加入 Trash Buster Simulator 的世界，成为变革的一部分！</p>",
